<p>BS-Alerts is a jQuery plugin that make it easy to create jQuery event based notification bar (warning, error, info, success) using <a href="https://twitter.github.com/bootstrap/" rel="nofollow">Twitter&nbsp;Bootstrap</a>&nbsp;and HTML5 <code>data-</code> attribute.</p>
